      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマス前のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nおやつは五百円以上買っても、いい？",
      "startTime": 3.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お、おやつ？\n一体なんの話を……あぁ、もしかして",
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "木組みの街でやる『ぱじゃパ！』のクリスマスライブに\n持って行くおやつが、なかなか決まらなくて",
      "startTime": 17.8117008369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "星見市と友好都市になった、木組みの街か\n……って、おやつを買う店ならあっちにもあるだろ？",
      "startTime": 25.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "星見市でしか買えないおやつを持って行けば\n木組みの街の人との、交流のきっかけになるかも……",
      "startTime": 32.9265316169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなら五百円とは言わずに\nいろいろ買って行ってもいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 40.2708393733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……！　確かに……。そうする\nネットで、木組みの街を調べたんだけど……",
      "startTime": 46.8647857826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく可愛くて、綺麗な街……実際に歩くのが楽しみ\nそれに、ライブ衣装のデザインも良かった",
      "startTime": 57.1314524492,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}